Hi,

Your email address has not yet been verified, which means that your possible registration for a Loop has not yet been completed.

You can click here to verify your email address or go to www.clothingloop.org and Log In. You do not need a password: enter your email address, you will be sent a unique link, when you click that link your email address is verified and you are logged in. 


Best wishes, the Clothing Loop team!
